commitResults.messageTitle: Upgrade sorting with multi-sort and sort by tag
commitResults.messageBody:
1. `sort t/TAG` now works (e.g. `sort t/friend`)
2. reverse sorting changed (e.g. `sort n/!`)
3. multi-sort now works (e.g. `sort t/friend n/!`)

For multi-sort, the first parameter will be used to sort the list.
The second parameter will act as a tiebreaker for the first parameter,
and so on.
